text: St. Joseph's Degree College, located in Kurnool, India, is governed by St. Joseph's Educational Society and registered under the Societies Registration Act XXI of 1860 in 1967. St. Joseph's Degree College is a self-financed college, without grant-in-aid. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Colleges in Andhra Pradesh Category:Universities and colleges in Kurnool district Category:Christian schools in Andhra Pradesh
